                    <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">M3 Pro</span>
                    <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">18GB RAM</span>
                </div>
